  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4381590/extras/b3cdd88f97088957fda55236ac94ca3e.avif?t=1774015972\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4381590/extras_big/b3cdd88f97088957fda55236ac94ca3e.webp?t=1774015972 width=1560 height=385 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll use various weapons to help you battle your way to the Ancient Strawberry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From an exploding snowball, to an instant death spoon, there are many ways you can fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll have to battle through hordes of monsters to get to the end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's only one life. If you die, you'll have to start from the beginning.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4381590/extras/b3cdd88f97088957fda55236ac94ca3e.avif?t=1774015972\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4381590/extras_big/b3cdd88f97088957fda55236ac94ca3e.webp?t=1774015972 width=1560 height=385 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll use various weapons to help you battle your way to the Ancient Strawberry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From an exploding snowball, to an instant death spoon, there are many ways you can fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll have to battle through hordes of monsters to get to the end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's only one life. If you die, you'll have to start from the beginning.</p>",
